rington CTLS]] (20)\n\n===Light Tank===\n* [[Renault FT]] (1)\n\n===Armoured cars===\n* [[Landsverk L180, L181 and L182|Landsverk L180]] (14)\n* [[Landsverk L180, L181 and L182|Landsverk L181]] (12)\n* [[M39 Pantserwagen]] (12)\n\n==New Zealand==\n\n===Converted tractors===\n* [[Bob Semple tank]] (4)\n\n===Light tanks===\n* [[Schofield tank|Light Tank, Wheel-and-Track (Schofield)]] wheel/caterpillar fast tank, prototype only\nAlso American M3 Stuart Tanks, called \"Honeys\" by the Brits and Commonwealth, used in Italy as recon vehicles\n\n=== Armoured personnel carriers ===\n* [[Universal carrier]] (1,300)\n\n=== Armoured cars ===\n* [[Standard Beaverette|Beaverette NZ]] (208) light armoured car similar to the British Beaverette\n\n==Norway==\n\n===Light tanks===\n* [[Stridsvagn L-120]] (1)\n\n==Poland==\n{{See also|list of Polish armoured fighting vehicles}}\n\n===Tankettes===\n* [[TKS|TK-3]] (280)\n* [[TKS]] (260)\n* TKS with 20&nbsp;mm gun (24)\n\n===Tanks===\n*[[4TP]]\n*[[7TP]] (162)\n*[[9TP]] (2 prototypes + 11 possible production models)\n*[[10TP]] (1 prototype)\n*14TP\n\n===Armored cars===\n* [[Samoch\u00f3d pancerny wz. 28]]\n* [[Samoch\u00f3d pancerny wz. 29]] (10-13)\n* [[Samoch\u00f3d pancerny wz. 34]] (87)\n* [[Kubu\u015b]] (1, used by the [[Polish Home Army]])\n\n===Self-propelled guns===\n* [[TKS-D]] (2)\n* TKD (4)\n\n===Artillery tractors===\n* [[C2P]] (200)\n* [[C4P]]\n* [[C7P]] (151)\n* [[PZIn\u017c 302]]\n\n===Utility vehicles===\n* [[Fiat 508 \u0142azik]]\n* [[Fiat 508/518]]\n* [[Fiat 518]]\n* [[Fiat 618]]\n* [[Fiat 621]]\n* [[Ursus A]]\n\n==Romania==\n\n===Tank destroyers===\n* [[TACAM T-60]] (34)\n* [[TACAM T-38]] (project)\n* [[TACAM R-1]] (project)\n* [[TACAM R-2]] (21)\n* [[V\u00e2n\u0103torul de care R35]] (30)\n* [[Mare\u0219al tank destroyer|Mare\u015fal]] (7 prototypes)\n\n===Tanks & Tankettes===\n* [[AH-IV|R-1]] (1 prototype + bought vehicles)\n* [[Panzerkampfwagen 35(t)|R-2]] (bought vehicles)\n* [[R-3 (tank)|R-3]] (project)\n* [[Renaul